Package stev.bowling

Parent package for all classes of the bowling project

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Frame
    Generic representation of a frame in a bowling game.
    Game
    A bowling game.
    GameDemo
    Simple file showing the usage of the Game and Frame objects to calculate and display the score in a bowling game.
    LastFrame
    Represents frame number 10 in a bowling game.
    NormalFrame
    Represents one of the first nine frames of a bowling game.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BowlingException
    Parent class of all exceptions thrown in the bowling project.
